  "expertise": "Business",
  "author": "Rho Lall",
  "keywords": "8th Habit, Steven Covey, business intelligence reporting, data driven decision making, data driven decisions, using data to make decisions",
  "short": "\nIn my early 20's my first blog failed before it ever started. I struggled with finding my voice. To be candid, I had a voice, just not one I could publish. I feared my voice would betray me as youthful, inexperienced, and stupid, because I was all these things. \n"
