var _frontmatter = {
  "title": "F*uck the Marshmallow: Greatness is Upon You",
  "date": "2018-06-29",
  "hero_image": "./media/business_f_the_marshmallow.png",
  "hero_alt": "F*uck the Marshmallow: Greatness is Upon You",
  "expertise": "Business",
  "author": "Rho Lall",
  "keywords": "business intelligence reporting, data driven decision making, data driven decisions, using data to make decisions",
  "short": " You might call this a rant.  This gets in the face of the American fable: work hard, persevere, succeed.  At first this new research was hard to swallow because I believe the fable.  But now, I’ve taken the time to ponder. Discomfort has subsided. Now I’m pissed. Separate the research from the politics. "
